<h2>About Dubai</h2>
<p>
Dubai is one of the most famous cities in the United Arab Emirates.
It is known for its modern architecture, luxury shopping, and vibrant nightlife.
Dubai has grown rapidly from a small desert town into a global city
for tourism, business, and technology.
</p>
</div>

<div class="section" id="places">
<h2>Famous Places</h2>
<ul>
<li>Burj Khalifa – The tallest building in the world</li>
<li>Palm Jumeirah – A man-made island shaped like a palm tree</li>
<li>Dubai Mall – One of the largest malls in the world</li>
<li>Dubai Marina – A beautiful waterfront city area</li>
</ul>
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/93/Burj_Khalifa.jpg" alt="Burj Khalifa">
