<div class="section" id="culture">
<h2>Culture</h2>
<p>
Dubai blends traditional Arab culture with modern lifestyles.
Visitors can experience desert safaris, traditional markets (souks),
Arabic food, and cultural festivals.
</p>
</div>

<div class="section" id="tourism">
<h2>Tourism</h2>
<p>
Tourists visit Dubai for luxury hotels, shopping festivals,
desert adventures, beaches, and world-class entertainment.
It is one of the most visited cities in the world.
</p>
